Text: How or what do u do with the patch nothing seems to work

worked great for me.  Probably should explain to some of us dummies on how to crack it.

Download SwishMax but dont open it.
Open patch, click on Swishmax on the right.
click on select file on left
then go to your Program Files folder
for Swish
Then click on Swish.exe file
then click on patch...

on the right it should say it is successful...
